---
title: Southern Cheesy Pork & Veggie Quesadillas with Garlic Aioli
description: Juicy Southern-spiced pork, sour cream and melted Cheddar cheese; it’s hard to resist these incredibly delicious quesadillas.
Plus, it takes less than 30 minutes to have this fun feast on your dinner table!
